{"tid":1005161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳工業邨發現疑似手榴彈 警封卡樂B廠房","createTime":"2019-02-02T04:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T08:51:07.000Z","uid":987,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2bff67b3fc466ac5eb6188a2bfaa5c0ce43c09","tid":1005161,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:27:22.000Z","msg":"早上9時許，將軍澳駿昌街9號卡樂B四洲有限公司香港工場，職員發現由法國入口的薯仔中，有懷疑手榴彈，大為緊張，報警求助。警方接報迅速到場了解事件，並召爆炸品處理課協助。<br />\n據了解，廠房的篩選機發現可疑物品，一個手榴彈狀的物體被泥封住，露出少許。職員將它拿到保安室，並報警處理。據知該手榴彈並無撞針，但有重量。<br />\n現場所見，廠房空地放有3個大鐵籠，內有近千個薯仔，都是同一批次，警員拉起封鎖線圍封住。<br />\n資料顯示，卡樂比與香港四洲集團於1976年合作，引入卡樂比蝦條、薯片及各款小食；1994年成立卡樂比四洲有限公司，設廠於西貢；2000年遷到將軍澳工業邨至今。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190202/59215176\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190202%2F59215176&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2QPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=63c98323\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190202%2F59215176&h=a1ab5f29\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190202/59215176</a>"},{"pid":"fed580ac0c1dea225c6da27436c84580eb283d7f","tid":1005161,"uid":116330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e6b1bb4dfb902bd0019541d37efb430c4a0193","tid":1005161,"uid":33875,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"原來薯片係咁炸出嚟"},{"pid":"1049b0deee2744c8a2a032dc9c3b43dd412551cc","tid":1005161,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:28:52.000Z","msg":"炸薯片<img src=\"/assets/f